short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Changes on SNYK UI to export, copy and improve navigation of vulnerabilities

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
With this extension you can get more data of SNYK service.

This extension help you to export/copy vulnerabilities score and details.
Also, generate useful links of project dependencies and its versions.
